"tag-moderation-wasitiyyah","tag-night-prayer-al-tahajjud","tag-prayer-al-salat","tag-rights-al-huquq","tag-sleep-al-nawm","tag-sunnah"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-5oC","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":35681,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/18\/uthman-fasting-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":20746,"position":0},"title":"Uthman on Martyrdom: Killed while fasting, breaks fast in Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 18, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Nafi\u2019 reported: Uthman, may Allah be pleased with him, saw the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, in his dream on the night he was killed the following morning. The Prophet said, \u201cO Uthman, break your fast with us tonight.\" Then, he was killed while he was fasting. Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27604,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/15\/huquq-family-voluntary-worship\/","url_meta":{"origin":20746,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Huquq: Rights of family over voluntary worship","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said to him, \u201cI am told you fast and never break your fast and you never stop praying at night? Fast and break your fast, pray at night, and sleep. Verily, your eyes deserve a share\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/categor